<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="screen-wrapper">

     <section>
     <h1>Welcome to Craft Tacos and Beer United</h1>
    </section>

     <section>

       <h4>You might think that the beauty of a taco recipe is that you hardly need one. Add anything that's delicious,
         tucked into a delicious tortilla, topped with whatever fits: some good protein, a squeeze of lime, a well-chosen salsa.
         But it can be nice to have a guide as you plot your next taco night. Below, you will find the most recent recipe submissions
         by our members and paired with their favorite craft beer to pair their taco creations.
         Sign up and join our community to create your recipes, write reviews, and share your favorite craft beer to pair with.
         <br>
         <br>
         Bon Appetitte and Cheers!


       </h4>
     </section>

     <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
         <% for (let i = 0; i < recipes.length; i++) { %>
            <div class="col s12 m6 card-wrapper card-container" onclick="location.href='/recipes/<%=recipes[i]._id%>'">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-image img-wrapper">
                  <img class="index-img" src="<%= recipes[i].image %>">
                  <a href="/recipes/<%= recipes[i]._id %>/edit" class="btn-floating halfway-fab waves-effect waves-light teal"><i class="material-icons">mode_edit</i></a>
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                  <span class="card-title"><%= recipes[i].name %></span>
                  <p><%= recipes[i].description %></p>
                  <div class="card-action">
                    <a href='/recipes/<%=recipes[i]._id%>'>See Full Recipe</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>




         <!-- <form action="/recipes/<%= recipes[i]._id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
            <input class="delete-button" type="submit" value="Delete" />
          </form> -->
          <!-- <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="/recipes/<%= recipes[i]._id %>/edit">Edit Recipe</a> -->
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  </body>
</html>
